    ]]></description>

    <change-notes><![CDATA[
      <p>2.0-RELEASE</p>
      <ul>
        <li>1.supports Arthas commands such as watch, trace, ognl static, ognl bean method, etc.</li>
      </ul>
      <ul>
        <li>1.支持Arthas 常用命令,比如 watch、trace、ognl static、ognl bean method</li>
